<HEADLINE>
THE GREENBACK'S SCARY SLIDE AGAINST THE YEN AND EURO  
 
</HEADLINE>
   (This excellent 750-word ``separate buy'' article is from the
current (week beginning 9 Jan. 1999) Economist magazine.)  
  
 (EDITORS: We regret that this material is NOT available to clients
