</P>
<P>
   5 households with income of $125,000 to $149,999
</P>
<P>
   0 households with income of over $150,000
</P>
<P>
   Source: U.S. Census Bureau
</P>
<P>
   ENDIT
</P>
<P>
   Story Filed By Cox Newspapers
</P>
