<DOCNO> NYT19990108.0105 </DOCNO>
<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-01-08 12:00 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A4649 &Cx1f; tad-z
u w &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-WEALTH-GAP-$ADV10-COX     01-08 0330
