<DOCNO> NYT19990108.0136 </DOCNO>
<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-01-08 14:10 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A4820 &Cx1f; tab-z
r l &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-SHOES-LIFEBEAT-ART-NY     01-08 1250
