Keeton Rylander says the state will have a $5.6 billion surplus
over the next two years. By R.G. RATCLIFFE.
</P>
<P>
   TEXAS-BODIES (Brownsville, Texas) _ Crews widening a roadway
near Brownsville, Texas, have unearthed 31 bodies. Officials are
tracing deeds and other documents in an attempt to identify them.
By JIM PINKERTON.
</P>
<P>
   TEXAS-DEATHROW (Austin, Texas) _ A Texas district court judge
rules that the policy of the State Board of Pardons and Parole to
review cases in secrecy does not violate the Constitution or state
laws. By CLAY ROBISON.
