try to dethrone John Elway and the Super Bowl champion Denver
Broncos in an AFC divisional playoff game on Saturday. By JOHN
McCLAIN.
</P>
<P>
   FBN-FALCONS (Atlanta) _ Over the past decade, the San Francisco
49ers have owned the Atlanta Falcons, winning 16 of the past 19
meetings. But the teams were all even at 1-1 this season, and the
14-2 Falcons are riding high with the home-field advantage heading
into Saturday's NFC playoff game. By JODY GOLDSTEIN.
</P>
