<DATE_TIME> 1999-01-08 20:42 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A5522 &Cx1f; tta-z
u s &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-OLY-BRIBERY-2TAKES-NY     01-08 1041
