   By Clare Farnsworth. (Story will move in the ``s'' category.)
</P>
<P>
   FBC-HAWKS-HOLMGREN (Undated) _ Tall and blessed with a strong
arm, Mike Holmgren was a prize quarterback recruit from San
Francisco, a new-age player for the option-minded '60s. The
6-foot-5 Holmgren chose USC and rarely got off the bench. The man
perceived to be an NFL genius, to have unfailing vision regarding
all matters pigskin, has not always made the soundest decisions.
</P>
<P>
   By Dan Raley. (Story will move in the ``s'' category.)
