<P>
   ABOUT-CARS-FERRARI (Undated) _ Selling Ferraris to Americans is
no longer just a matter of flattering the customers and wearing
Armani suits really well. While the current models knock-down
gorgeous, they are also far more expensive than the Porsches, and
Jaguars that can be nearly as alluring. By Peter Passell. (Moved).
