<DOCTYPE> MISCELLANEOUS TEXT (slug-filter) </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-01-08 22:49 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A5691 &Cx1f; taf-z
u f &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-BIZGLANCE-NYT &LR;      01-08 0678
